              their risk for engaging in violence or other harmful activities, and identifying intervention strategies to
              manage that risk.</p>
            <a href="#">K-12 School Security: A Guide for Preventing and Protecting against Gun Violence (2<sup>nd</sup>
              ed., 2018)</a>
            <p>This guide provides preventive and protective measures to address the threat of gun violence in schools.
