          <div id="a3" class="usa-accordion__content usa-prose" hidden="">
            <p>Soft targets include any person or thing that is relatively unprotected or vulnerable to a terrorist attack
              or an act of violence. Soft targets on college and university campuses today present a unique challenge
              given the large number of on- and off-campus populations, often resulting in crowded public areas. IHEs
              should use these resources to prepare for a potential soft target attack against crowded places.</p>
